<lb ed="C I" n="0088a00"/><milestone n="1" unit="juan"/><head type="no">No. 35</head>
<lb ed="C I" n="0088a00"/><juan n="001" fun="open"><mulu n="001" type="卷"/><jhead><title>張法壽息榮遷等造像記</title></jhead></juan>
<lb ed="C I" n="0088a00"/><mulu level="1" label="之一　碑側" type="其他"/><head>之一　碑側</head>
<div2>
<lb ed="C I" n="0088a01"/><p id="pI01p0088a0101">夫靈真玄廓。妙絕難測。非言莫能宣其<note n="0088001" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB08073;＝旨【史】</note><app n="0088001"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">旨</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB08073;</rdg></app>。非像無以表其狀。言宣二六
<lb ed="C I" n="0088a02"/>之教。像跡四八之<note n="0088002" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30605;＝璃【史】</note><app n="0088002"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">璃</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30605;</rdg></app>。豈不淵玄<note n="0088003" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB00287;＝沖【史】</note><app n="0088003"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">沖</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB00287;</rdg></app>漠。巍巍惟極者哉。是以務聖寺檀主
<lb ed="C I" n="0088a03"/>張法壽。能於五蓋重羅之下。<note n="0088004" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB01438;＝契【史】</note><app n="0088004"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">契</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB01438;</rdg></app>斷<note n="0088005" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30606;＝恩【史】</note><app n="0088005"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">恩</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30606;</rdg></app>愛塵勞之繒網。於熙平二年。捨宅
<lb ed="C I" n="0088a04"/>造寺。宿願磛像。福不止已。<note n="0088006" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB02420;＝規【史】</note><app n="0088006"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">規</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB02420;</rdg></app>度法界。尋其羅絡。情苞聖境。自非藉因積
<lb ed="C I" n="0088a05"/>劫。英貴累世者。熟能發茲宏闊願行者焉。息榮遷。脩和。行慈仁孝。世習
<lb ed="C I" n="0088a06"/>精<note n="0088007" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30607;＝懿【史】</note><app n="0088007"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">懿</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30607;</rdg></app>。志慕幽寂。妙真遐願。刊石建像。釋迦文佛。觀音。文殊。仰述亡考。平
<lb ed="C I" n="0088a07"/>康<note n="0088008" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30608;＝舊【史】</note><app n="0088008"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">舊</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30608;</rdg></app>願。復於像側。隱出<app><lem wit="【CBETA】" resp="CBETA.maha">&CB07099;</lem><rdg wit="【原】【史】">旡</rdg></app>量壽佛。福洽法界。考妣等神。捨茲質形。<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">悉</unclear>
<lb ed="C I" n="0088a08"/><note n="0088009" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30609;＝稟【史】</note><app n="0088009"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">稟</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30609;</rdg></app>淨境。同<note n="0088010" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30610;＝曉【史】</note><app n="0088010"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">曉</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30610;</rdg></app>薩雲。覺道成佛。
<lb ed="C I" n="0088a09"/>　　　　　　大魏天平二年歲次乙卯四月十一日比丘洪寶銘</p>
</div2>
</div1>
<div1>
<lb ed="C I" n="0088b00"/><mulu level="1" label="之二　碑陰" type="其他"/><head>之二　碑陰</head>
<div2>
<lb ed="C I" n="0088b01"/><p id="pI01p0088b0101">
<lb ed="C I" n="0088b02"/>
<lb ed="C I" n="0088b03"/>
<lb ed="C I" n="0088b04"/>金山寶蓋如來　范定洛南方寶相如來　文殊師利佛主張義容　普光佛主毛元姜　大通智勝佛主衛僧副　帝相佛主尹文敬為父母　寶華功德海琉<app source="0088002" type="＊"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">璃</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30605;</rdg></app>金山光明如來主寇令容
<lb ed="C I" n="0088b05"/>
<lb ed="C I" n="0088b06"/>金炎光明如來　車河興東方阿&CB00434;如來　阿彌陀佛主董元士　日月燈明佛主楊塔　須彌頂佛張仲華為父母梵相佛主楊聖鬘　光明如來主曹佛光
<lb ed="C I" n="0088b07"/>
<lb ed="C I" n="0088b08"/>
<lb ed="C I" n="0088b09"/>光明王相如來主張桃奉寶勝如來奉為父母　　　　　　　　　　　藥師琉<app source="0088002" type="＊"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">璃</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30605;</rdg></app>光佛楊元寄　師子音佛主宋文勝　多摩羅跋栴檀香神通佛名相如來二佛主榮千
<lb ed="C I" n="0088b10"/>
<lb ed="C I" n="0088b11"/>
<lb ed="C I" n="0088b12"/>&CB07099;垢熾寶如來主曇景　寶相如來主權荊珍　釋迦多寶二佛范<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">佛</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">保</unclear>　難勝佛張遵為父母　虛空住佛主田貴洛　須彌相佛董龍國為父母閻浮那提金光如來
<lb ed="C I" n="0088b13"/>
<lb ed="C I" n="0088b14"/>
<lb ed="C I" n="0088b15"/>難勝如來主僧真　大炬如來主咎寄保　北微妙聲佛崔進合家　觀世音佛主劉道亮　常滅佛　　　　　　　　雲自在佛董歸樂為母　多摩羅跋旃檀香佛
<lb ed="C I" n="0088b16"/>
<lb ed="C I" n="0088b17"/>
<lb ed="C I" n="0088b18"/>□□如來主惠照　金華炎光<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">相</unclear>如來主田佛光　西&CB07099;量<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">壽</unclear>．．．．<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">那</unclear>佛主段崑崙　華光佛主路法奴<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">雲</unclear>　自在王佛段邕為亡息鼠兒　寶藏佛張世伯為亡母</p>
</div2>
<div2>
<lb ed="C I" n="0088c01"/><p id="pI01p0088c0101">董大醜
<lb ed="C I" n="0088c02"/>董清頭
<lb ed="C I" n="0088c03"/>董夏歡
<lb ed="C I" n="0088c04"/>
<lb ed="C I" n="0088c05"/>願元王崇禮兄弟
<lb ed="C I" n="0088c06"/>五人悉得善集大
<lb ed="C I" n="0088c07"/>家范度內外七世
<lb ed="C I" n="0088c08"/>父母法界倉生成佛
<lb ed="C I" n="0088c09"/>張榮千為存亡二
<lb ed="C I" n="0088c10"/>弟南方字榮和
<lb ed="C I" n="0088c11"/>身康常貴亡者
<lb ed="C I" n="0088c12"/>遇佛法界成佛
<lb ed="C I" n="0088c13"/>張桃棒造二佛
<lb ed="C I" n="0088c14"/>一佛為亡父母<app source="0088008" type="＊"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">舊</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30608;</rdg></app>
<lb ed="C I" n="0088c15"/>願造一佛為法
<lb ed="C I" n="0088c16"/>界眾生一切父母
<lb ed="C I" n="0088c17"/>
<lb ed="C I" n="0088c18"/></p>
</div2>
